# Drums
sfx kick on noise
  volume 9 9 4 2
  pitch 10 0

sfx snare on noise
  volume 10 8 6 4 3 2 1
  pitch 4 10

sfx tkick on triangle
  volume 15 15 15 2
  pitch e' c' a f#

sfx tsnare on triangle
  volume 15 15
  pitch b' a'

sfx clhat on noise
  timbre | 0 1
  volume 6 3 1
  pitch 12

drum kick kick tkick
drum snare snare tsnare
drum clhat clhat

